    dc:creator "Dang, Li-Hong; Mound, Laurence A.; Qiao, Ge-Xia" ;
    dc:date "2013" ;
    dc:title "Leaf-litter thrips of the genus Adraneothrips from Asia and Australia (Thysanoptera, Phlaeothripinae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.284907>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.284909>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.284912>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.284911>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.284913>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.284914>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.284908>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.284915> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.284907>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 9. Adraneothrips adult colour patterns. (1) braccatus; (2) chinensis; (3) coloratus; (4) darwini; (5) disjunctus; (6) hani; (7) limpidus; (8) makilingensis; (9) nilgiriensis." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/284907/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.284909>
    dc:description "FIGURES 16 – 21. Adraneothrips heads. (16) braccatus; (17) chinensis; (18) coloratus; (19) darwini; (20) hani; (21); makilingensis." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/284909/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.284912>
    dc:description "FIGURES 33 – 39. Adraneothrips species. Male sternite VIII 33 – 36: (33) braccatus; (34) chinensis; (35) makilingensis; (36) russatus. (37) limpidus pronotum. Chaetotaxy of tergite IX 38 – 39: (38) hani male; (39) limpidus female." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/284912/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.284911>
    dc:description "FIGURES 26 – 32. Adraneothrips metanota and tergites. (26) braccatus; (27) coloratus; (28) darwini; (29) russatus; (30) hani; (31) waui; (32) yunnanensis." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/284911/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.284913>
    dc:description "FIGURES 40 – 47. Adraneothrips darwini sp. n. Female: (40) dorsal view of head, pronotum and foreleg; (41) antenna; (43) dorsal view of mesonotum & metanotum; (44) base of fore wing; (45) dorsal view of abdominal tergites IX – X; (46) pelta; (47) mesopraesternum. Male: (42) abdominal sternite VIII and tergites IX – X." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/284913/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.284914>
    dc:description "FIGURES 48 – 57. Adraneothrips hani sp. n. Female: (48) antenna; (49) dorsal view of head and pronotum; (50) dorsal view of mesonotum & metanotum; (51) mesopraesternum; (52) base of forewing; (53) pelta; (56) abdominal tergite V; (57) dorsal view of abdominal tergites IX – X. Male: (54) abdominal tergites IX – X; (55) abdominal sternum VIII pore plate." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/284914/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.284908>
    dc:description "FIGURES 10 – 15. Adraneothrips adult colour patterns. (10) pteris; (11) russatus (Australia); (12) russatus (China); (13) stannardi; (14) waui; (15) yunnanensis." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/284908/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.284915>
    dc:description "FIGURES 58 – 65. Adraneothrips makilingensis. Female: (58) dorsal view of head and pronotum; (59) antenna; (60) dorsal view of abdominal tergites IX – X; (62) dorsal view of mesonotum & metanotum; (63) mesopraesternum; (64) base of forewing. Male: (61) abdominal tergites IX – X; (65) abdominal sternum VIII pore plate." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/284915/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

